  "id": "RAW_a8de0f71",
  "title": "今日开源（2026-3-17）：NVIDIA 发布 Nemotron-3-Nano 模型，融合 Mamba-2 与注意力层实现一体化任务处理",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501825&idx=1&sn=05299b7347041062538f30eddd8d09a7",
  "date": "2026-03-17 10:31:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Nemotron-3-Nano</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1216\" data-imgfileid=\"100018169\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a0b089e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFY3yNiayYDAwftHicQYoiaAh5upvBdn4dAqQhVxe9RVrVdzmJ5aUTr0pSpmwZ2W6D0D9FgjR0eqX9BcbQib1EBP0ibBP0wNRswhbmRc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nemotron-3-Nano是由NVIDIA从头训练的小型语言模型，旨在统一处理推理和非推理任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">生成推理轨迹</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来响应用户查询，并最终给出答案。用户可以通过系统提示控制模型的推理能力。该模型采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">混合架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，主要由Mamba-2和MLP层组成，并结合了四个注意力层。它支持英语，并已通过Qwen进行改进，适用于商业用途。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-3-nano\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-3-nano</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：LTX-2.3 NVFP4</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"884\" data-imgfileid=\"100018171\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7453fa22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFalRgOb3GNFKlicKLBDauep2qibmbTJlJJMoNc6cXwiaibdmichVHiarbmiao1pcjX7vELfp4gpQ2j09ibBdu0R8pvt1iacngVIQEe5d2ME%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LTX-2.3 NVFP4是一个基于DiT的音视频基础模型，旨在通过单一模型生成同步的视频和音频。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型是LTX-2的重要更新，提升了音频和视觉质量，并增强了对提示的遵循能力。它结合了现代视频生成的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">核心构建模块</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，具有开放的权重，专注于实际的本地执行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ltx-2-3-nvfp4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ltx-2-3-nvfp4</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：HiAR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45092592592592595\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"722\" data-imgfileid=\"100018167\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2aad7320&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZR1630MCMzm1cPESdT5hgQbgqlT26lXz82maqtCKm4cLMfe7fKicwicBch8FTuhDG5n35ZYch17uNY6TswVaWdbZiclQqx4iblnX0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★HiAR是一种层次自回归视频生成模型，通过流水线并行推理实现视频生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型改变了传统的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">块优先去噪方式</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，采用了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">步骤优先</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的层次调度，每个块在相同噪声水平上依赖于早期块，从而减少长时间漂移并保持时间连续性。HiAR的设计还包括一个专用的前向KL正则化器，以在自回归展开过程中保持运动多样性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hiar\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hiar</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Browser</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5787037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"926\" data-imgfileid=\"100018168\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=31f3b7f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZ17wlQAI8NErx9VR7XXaUo9ueSU6w0aGGy8VTLFQr5ibhWjccnYedWng3WlnFaf0YNwVNmcYSgwAicdvshMibxpnVoibic7Oib5kWO4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Browser是Lightpanda的一个专为AI Agent和自动化设计的无头浏览器。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它不是Chromium的分支，也不是WebKit的补丁，而是用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Zig语言</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">从头构建的新浏览器。该浏览器支持JavaScript执行和部分Web API，兼容Playwright、Puppeteer和chromedp。Lightpanda以其</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">超低的内存占用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">极快的执行速度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，适用于快速的Web自动化、AI Agent、LLM训练、抓取和测试任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/browser\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/browser</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：FedDRM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.674074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1079\" data-imgfileid=\"100018170\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=876049bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbZo5FdxIibL8mVhebZRN9Naj8n3aiadVicgfM7NagMvhKAj9bH6VxxqJ2DVqA9GfJGqCVc1AicnE1J62ZyZvex1WbuuobesMRvrjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FedDRM该项目提出了一种新的联邦学习（FL）范式，旨在解决数据分布在不同客户端之间显著变化的问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过引入</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">密度比模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">经验似然框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，项目不仅提高了每个客户端的本地模型效果，还能为新任务或查询找到最佳匹配的客户端。实验结果表明，该框架在基准数据集上提高了模型准确性和客户端指导的精确性，为构建更智能和资源高效的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">FL系统</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">开辟了新方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/feddrm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/feddrm</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Leanstral</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100018172\" data-ratio=\"0.5277777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d797d377&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbxyhyxHDR428615GYLxlTxH2FRz1eTibJrTLkSvbOicPdJicAFicUT0ib7NGUtChMObnOZD6W66GeTouxUxB47IrYsSNYS0WFxRicFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Leanstral是首个为Lean 4设计的开源代码Agent，Lean 4是一种能够表达复杂数学对象和软件规范的证明助手。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Leanstral结合了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">高效架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，使其在性能和成本效益上优于现有的闭源替代品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/leanstral\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/leanstral</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月 17 日的开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了 NVIDIA 的 Nemotron-3-Nano 混合架构模型、音视频生成模型 LTX-2.3 以及专为 Agent 设计的 Zig 语言无头浏览器。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月 17 日的开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了 NVIDIA 的 Nemotron-3-Nano 混合架构模型、音视频生成模型 LTX-2.3 以及专为 Agent 设计的 Zig 语言无头浏览器。",
